Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.36,0:02:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates vying for the One Piece\Nhead for the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.10,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,People call it the "New World."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the only one to ever conquer\Nthese waters was the Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.48,0:03:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, the boy whose body turned to rubber\Nafter eating the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey D. Luffy and his crew\Nventure into that very sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.70,0:03:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,After surviving a fierce battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,the Straw Hats reach the New World at long last,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the harshest sea, ruled by the Four Emperors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.01,0:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They landed on Punk Hazard—an island divided into the Burning and Frozen Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,After learning of the island's ruler, Caesar Clown's, true intentions,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,they are now trying\Nto escape Netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Alongside their newfound ally, the Warlord Trafalgar Law,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.29,0:03:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,they are now on the move to kidnap Caesar,\Nsave the children, and escape from the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.44,0:03:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside a garbage dump, Luffy met a dragon named Momonosuke,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.15,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,who shares a name with the boy\NKin'emon the samurai had been searching for.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're... flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Mocha!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.49,0:04:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Pirate Hunter Zoro
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,with a 120-million-berry bounty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a Logia-type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take care of her!
